    "raw_text": "Hi @ngoldbaum I am happy if you want to quote me in the way you did, but I think the first quote detracts from your point due to my mistake of calling the free-threaded version *experimental*, when it is not. What I meant is that there is no stable API that would avoid having to build wheels for each new version of Python, which is precisely what I wish to avoid. Feel free to paraphrase me instead of quoting me.\r\n",
